  "slug": "portal-gels",
  "title": "Portal Gels",
  "description": "Adds movement gels from Portal 2.",
  "body": "<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/236/portal_gels_logo_transparent.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"446\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/736/0/11gels_logo.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"316\" /><br /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1200/983/2025-05-26_03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"648\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Portal Gels mod adds Repulsion, Propulsion and Converion Gels from Portal 2 game!</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>And also 3 new types of Repulsion Gel that can be obtained only in Creative.</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Subscribe on mod's platforms:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://discord.gg/TpP4vAMDgb\">Discord Server</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@unknownraccooneternaltales4940\">YouTube</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a title=\"Telegramm channel\" href=\"https://t.me/eternal_tales_news\">Telegram channel</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://eternaltales.wiki.gg/wiki/Eternal_Tales_Wiki\">Wiki</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><a href=\"https://vk.com/eternal_tales\">VK (Russian)&nbsp;</a></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"font-size: 1.2rem;\">&nbsp;</span><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/233/5c67715083a696dc585fbca3dd2b4bbd.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"255\" /></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><iframe allowfullscreen=\"allowfullscreen\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/kcc-F_N3FxQ?wmode=transparent\" height=\"358\" width=\"638\"></iframe></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://imgur.com/qRj0YmO\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DgKDEKO.mp4\" alt=\"\" /><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRj0YmO.gifv\" alt=\"\" /></strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRj0YmO.gifv\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/234/06bbee047e7cebe3f9db8afb0380894d.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"184\" /><strong>Increases player's jump height and repulse you when you fall on it</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qRj0YmO.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/235/fa19cad9621233b691e3358ba9b1c552.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"164\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>Accelerate the player. And it also good with Propulsion Gel. When you run Repulsion Gel automatically repulse you saving your running speed for longer jump.</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/iQ5HfSc.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"633\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><em>Adhesion Gel</em></strong> - slows the player down. This gel was orininally scrapped from Portal 2 but was found in game files.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Conversion Gel</em></strong> - needed to make other gels.</p>\n<p><strong><em>Cleansing Gel</em></strong> - it's drop wash any other Gels.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>And some gels I come up with when test Repulsion Gel. They're have some interesting functions and available only in Creative.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/237/6c26182e301b3c2b53d4692f2dbb50bf.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"124\" /><strong>Repulse you even if you don't jump on it</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/FquxMVG.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/238/0d00e732659078a216eafd999c671755.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"126\" /><strong>Has no jump height limit</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/D9vEyfC.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/621/239/611f6fcee0fb5027af0d95e07fddf488.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"134\" />Increases height with every jump</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/DgKDEKO.gif\" alt=\"\" width=\"690\" height=\"388\" /></strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1200/983/2025-05-26_03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"648\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>New Gels:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">From left to right:&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Super Slowing Gel (Brown) - slows you down very much<br />- Portalize Gel (Yellow) - teleports you in random location in 10 blocks radius<br /></span><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Slowing Gel (Green) - slows you down<br />- Igniting Gel (Red) - ignites you<br />- Black Hole (Black) - teleports you under the blocks<br />- Reflection Gel (White) - reflects the projectiles. This Gel was in original Portal 2 during development but was removed<br /><br /><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/1200/984/2025-05-26_03.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1125\" height=\"648\" /><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Advanced Knee Replacements and Long Fall Boots<br /></strong><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Boots from Portal that removes any damage from falling</span></span></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://imgur.com/DgKDEKO\" alt=\"\" /></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><strong>Some answers for possible questions:</strong></span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Can someone add this mod to modpack or map?</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Of course, but add credits and tell me about this. I'm interesting in projects using my mod.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">&nbsp;</p>",
